(ns farsund.flex
  (:require [cljs.spec.alpha :as s]
            [reagent.core :as r]
            [reagent.ratom :refer [reaction]]
            [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [cuerdas.core :as str]
            [taoensso.encore :as e]))


(declare box hbox vbox)


(def ^:private all-prop-keys
  [:size :justify-content :align-items :align-self
   :flex-wrap :flex-direction
   :min-width :width :max-width
   :min-height :height :max-height
   :color :gap :gap-interleave? :overflow
   :overflow-x :overflow-y
   :xl :<=xl :>=lg :lg :<=lg :>=md :md :<=md :>=sm :sm :<=sm :>=xs :xs
   :spacing])


(defn display
  ([style]
   (merge style {:display :flex}))
  ([]
   (display {})))

(s/def ::direction (s/and (s/conformer #(if (keyword? %) (name %) %))
                          #{"row" "row-rewerse" "column" "column-rewerse"}))
(s/def ::wrap (s/nilable (s/and (s/conformer #(if (keyword? %) (name %) %)) #{"wrap" "nowrap"})))
(s/def ::flow (s/or :string (s/and string? #(let [[direction wrap] (str/split % " ")]
                                              (or (and (s/valid? ::direction direction)
                                                       (s/valid? ::wrap wrap))
                                                  (s/valid? #{"inherit"} %))))
                    :coll (s/and vector? (s/cat :direction ::direction :wrap ::wrap)
                                 (s/conformer (fn [{:keys [direction wrap]}] (str direction " " wrap))))))
(s/def ::justify #{:flex-start :flex-end :center :space-between :space-around})
(s/def ::align #{:flex-start :flex-end :center :stretch :baseline})


(defn direction
  ([style dir]
   (merge style {:flex-direction (s/conform ::direction dir)}))
  ([dir]
   (direction {} dir)))


(defn wrap
  ([style x]
   (merge style {:flex-wrap (s/conform ::wrap x)}))
  ([x]
   (wrap {} x)))


(defn flow
  ([style flow]
   (merge style {:flex-flow (second (s/conform ::flow flow))}))
  ([flow]
   (flow {} flow)))


(defn justify-content
  ([style alignment]
   (if alignment
     (merge style {:justify-content (s/conform ::justify alignment)})
     style))
  ([alignment]
   (justify-content {} alignment)))


(defn align-items
  ([style alignment]
   (if alignment
     (merge style {:align-items (s/conform ::align alignment)})
     style))
  ([alignment]
   (align-items {} alignment)))


(defn align-self
  ([style alignment]
   (if alignment
     (merge style {:align-self (s/conform alignment ::align)})
     style))
  ([alignment]
   (align-self {} alignment)))


(defn align-content
  ([style alignment]
   (if alignment
     (merge style {:align-content (s/conform ::justify alignment)})
     style))
  ([alignment]
   (align-content {} alignment)))


(defn order
  ([style ord]
   (merge style {:order ord}))
  ([ord]
   (order {} ord)))


(s/def ::px #(re-find #"px" %))
(s/def ::% #(re-find #"\%" %))
(s/def :flex/initial #{"initial" :initial})
(s/def :flex/auto #{"auto" :auto})
(s/def :flex/none #{"none" :none})
(s/def :flex/grow (s/or :number number? :string str/numeric?))
(s/def :flex/shrink (s/or :number number? :string str/numeric?))
(s/def :flex/basis (s/or :px ::px
                         :percent ::%
                         :auto :flex/auto
                         :initial :flex/initial))
(s/def :flex/gsb (s/or :string
                       (s/and string? #(let [[g s b] (str/split %)]
                                         (and (s/valid? :flex/grow g)
                                              (s/valid? :flex/shrink s)
                                              (s/valid? :flex/basis b))))
                       :coll
                       (s/and (s/cat :grow :flex/grow :shrink :flex/shrink :basis :flex/basis)
                              (s/conformer (fn [m] (str/join " " (map second (vals m))))))))

(s/def :flex/flex (s/nilable
                    (s/or :auto :flex/auto
                          :initial :flex/initial
                          :none :flex/none
                          :grow :flex/grow
                          :gsb :flex/gsb
                          :basis :flex/basis)))

(s/def ::spacing (s/or :one int? :coll (s/+ int?)))


(defn media-size [{:keys [xl <=xl >=lg lg <=lg >=md md <=md >=sm sm <=sm >=xs xs size]} bp]
  (let [result (case bp
                 :xl (or xl <=xl >=lg >=md >=sm >=xs size lg <=lg md <=md sm <=sm xs)
                 :lg (or lg >=lg <=lg >=md <=xl >=sm >=xs size md <=md sm <=sm xs)
                 :md (or md >=md <=md <=lg >=sm <=xl >=xs size sm <=sm xs)
                 :sm (or sm >=sm <=sm >=xs <=md <=lg <=xl size xs)
                 :xs (or xs >=xs <=sm <=md <=lg <=xl size)
                 nil)]
    result))


(defn ->px [v & vs]
  (str/trim
    (reduce
      (fn [acc v] (str acc v "px "))
      (str v "px ")
      vs)))


(defn ->spacing
  ([style v]
   (let [[t v] (s/conform ::spacing v)]
     (case t
       :one (merge style {:padding (->px (/ v 2))})
       :coll (merge style {:padding (apply ->px (map #(/ % 2) v))}))))
  ([v]
   (->spacing {} v)))


(defn flex
  ([style size]
   (if size
     (let [[type size] (s/conform :flex/flex size)
           flex (case type
                  :initial "0 1 auto"
                  :auto "1 1 auto"
                  :none "0 0 auto"
                  :grow (str (last size) " 1 0px")
                  :basis (let [[unit size] size]
                           (case unit
                             :px (str "0 0 " size)
                             :percent (str "0 0 " size)))
                  :gsb (second size)
                  size)]
       (merge style
              {:flex flex}))
     style))
  ([size]
   (flex {} size)))


(defn add-spacing [spacing [obj & objs :as elems]]
  (when-not (empty? elems)
    (let [m (meta elems)
          elems (filter identity objs)
          [props & objs] (if (map? (first elems)) elems [{} elems])]
      (if (#{farsund.flex/box farsund.flex/hbox farsund.flex/vbox} obj)
        (into [obj (->spacing (if (map? props) props {}) spacing)] objs)
        (with-meta [box (->spacing {:size :auto} spacing) (into [obj props] objs)] m)))))


(defn gap [{:keys [size] :as args}]
  (let [this (r/current-component)
        bp (rf/subscribe [:window/breakpoint])
        size (reaction (or (media-size args @bp) size))]
    (fn [{:keys [width height]}]
      (let [props (reduce dissoc (r/props this) all-prop-keys)
            children (r/children this)]
        (when-not (= :hide @size)
          (into [:div (r/merge-props props
                                     {:style (-> {}
                                                 (e/assoc-some :width (or width size)
                                                               :height (or height size))
                                                 (flex @size))})]
            children))))))

(defn gap-interpose
  [size children]
  (let [gap-form [farsund.flex/gap {:size size}]]
    (into [] (interpose gap-form) children)))


(defn line [{:keys [size color]
             :or   {color "lightgray"}}]
  (let [this (r/current-component)]
    (fn [{:keys [size color]
          :or   {color "lightgray"}}]
      (let [props (apply dissoc (r/props this) all-prop-keys)
            children (r/children this)]
        (into [:div (r/merge-props props
                                   {:style (flex {:background-color color} size)})]
          children)))))


(defn scroller [{:keys [size overflow overflow-x overflow-y]
                 :or   {size :auto}
                 :as   args}]
  (let [this (r/current-component)
        not-v-or-h (and (nil? overflow-y) (nil? overflow-x))
        overflow (if (and (nil? overflow) not-v-or-h) :auto overflow)
        bp (rf/subscribe [:window/breakpoint])
        size (reaction (or (media-size args @bp) size))]
    (fn [{:keys [justify-content align-items align-self gap
                 min-width width max-width
                 min-height height max-height
                 overflow-x overflow-y]}]
      (let [props (apply dissoc (r/props this) all-prop-keys)
            children (r/children this)]
        (when-not (= :hide @size)
          (into [:div (r/merge-props props
                                     {:style (-> {}
                                                 (e/assoc-some :min-width min-width
                                                               :width width
                                                               :max-width max-width
                                                               :min-height min-height
                                                               :height height
                                                               :max-height max-height
                                                               :overflow overflow
                                                               :overflow-x overflow-x
                                                               :overflow-y overflow-y)
                                                 (display)
                                                 (flex @size)
                                                 (flow "inherit")
                                                 (farsund.flex/justify-content justify-content)
                                                 (farsund.flex/align-items align-items)
                                                 (farsund.flex/align-self align-self))})]
            children))))))


(defn box [{:keys [size]
            :or   {size :none}
            :as   args}]
  (let [this (r/current-component)
        bp (rf/subscribe [:window/breakpoint])
        size (reaction (or (media-size args @bp) size))]
    (fn [{:keys [justify-content align-items align-self
                 min-width width max-width min-height
                 height max-height]
          :or   {justify-content :start align-items :stretch size :none}
          :as   args}]
      ;(println :rerender :box)
      (let [props (apply dissoc (r/props this) all-prop-keys)
            children (into [] (filter identity) (r/children this))]
        (when-not (= :hide @size)
          (into [:div (r/merge-props props
                                     {:id    :box
                                      :style (-> {}
                                                 (e/assoc-some :min-width min-width
                                                               :width width
                                                               :max-width max-width
                                                               :min-height min-height
                                                               :height height
                                                               :max-height max-height)
                                                 (display)
                                                 (flex @size)
                                                 (flow "inherit")
                                                 (farsund.flex/justify-content justify-content)
                                                 (farsund.flex/align-items align-items)
                                                 (farsund.flex/align-self align-self))})]
            children))))))


(defn hbox [{:keys [size] :or {size :none} :as args}]
  (let [this (r/current-component)
        bp (rf/subscribe [:window/breakpoint])
        size (reaction (or (media-size args @bp) size))]
    (fn [{:keys [justify-content align-items align-self direction wrap
                 min-width width max-width min-height
                 height max-height gap]
          :or   {justify-content :start align-items :stretch direction :row wrap :nowrap}}]
      (let [props (apply dissoc (r/props this) all-prop-keys)
            children (into [] (filter identity) (r/children this))
            children (cond->> children gap (gap-interpose gap))]
        ;(println :rerender :hbox)
        (when-not (= :hide @size)
          (into [:div (r/merge-props props
                                     {:id    :hbox
                                      :style (-> {}
                                                 (e/assoc-some :min-width min-width
                                                               :width width
                                                               :max-width max-width
                                                               :min-height min-height
                                                               :height height
                                                               :max-height max-height)
                                                 (display)
                                                 (flex @size)
                                                 (flow [direction wrap])
                                                 (farsund.flex/justify-content justify-content)
                                                 (farsund.flex/align-items align-items)
                                                 (farsund.flex/align-self align-self))})]
            children))))))



(defn vbox [{:keys [size] :or {size :none} :as args}]
  (let [this (r/current-component)
        bp (rf/subscribe [:window/breakpoint])
        size (reaction (or (media-size args @bp) size))]
    (fn [{:keys [justify-content align-items align-self direction wrap
                 min-width width max-width min-height
                 height max-height gap]
          :or   {justify-content :start align-items :stretch size :none direction :column wrap :nowrap}}]
      ;(println :rerender :vbox)
      (let [props (apply dissoc (r/props this) all-prop-keys)
            children (into [] (filter identity) (r/children this))
            children (cond->> children gap (gap-interpose gap))]
        (when-not (= :hide @size)
          (into [:div (r/merge-props props
                                     {:id    :vbox
                                      :style (-> {}
                                                 (e/assoc-some :min-width min-width
                                                               :width width
                                                               :max-width max-width
                                                               :min-height min-height
                                                               :height height
                                                               :max-height max-height)
                                                 (display)
                                                 (flex @size)
                                                 (flow [direction wrap])
                                                 (farsund.flex/justify-content justify-content)
                                                 (farsund.flex/align-items align-items)
                                                 (farsund.flex/align-self align-self))})]
            children))))))
